Package gameClient

Class Pokemon

java.lang.Object
gameClient.Pokemon
public class Pokemon
extends java.lang.Object
This class is a representation of Pokemon in the Pokemons Game. most of the data are coming from the server as Json, and there data that coming from the client, like _edge and graph.
